%^BOLD%^-=%^RESET%^%^CYAN%^Madness Domain%^BOLD%^%^WHITE%^=-%^RESET%^

You embrace the madness that lurks deep in your heart, and can unleash it to drive your foes insane or to sacrifice certain abilities to hone others.

The madness domain contains the following spells:

Cause Fear, Touch Of Idiocy, Rage, Confusion, Nightmare, Phantasmal Killer, Insanity, Scintillating Pattern, Weird

%^CYAN%^Deities%^RESET%^: The Faceless One

%^BOLD%^Please see individual help files for an explanation of what each spell does.%^RESET%^
